title: Stacey Abrams | Late Night Democratic Presidential Debate: New Hampshire
description:
Seth moderates another high-stakes debate between the 2020 Democratic presidential candidates.

He also talks to Stacey Abrams, former Georgia gubernatorial candidate and founder of Fair Fight 2020. She also takes a few more questions backstage exclusively for this podcast.
